in Glee Club today,

180
00:06:22,367 --> 00:06:23,617
and it was a total disaster.

181
00:06:23,651 --> 00:06:25,852
What happened?
I don't know.

182
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,020
I mean, the lesson
that I planned

183
00:06:27,038 --> 00:06:28,021
was awesome.

184
00:06:28,039 --> 00:06:29,323
I... I think
it's just that the...

185
00:06:29,357 --> 00:06:31,358
