190
00:06:38,132 --> 00:06:40,033
but maybe you should invest
in a pair of tights.

191
00:06:40,051 --> 00:06:42,002
You know, Clark Kent
was an awesome guy,

192
00:06:42,036 --> 00:06:45,372
but it was Superman
who inspired everyone.

193
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:47,474
