remember?

200
00:07:04,993 --> 00:07:08,028
No more bullying, blackmail
or assault this year.

201
00:07:08,062 --> 00:07:09,830
That must be boring for you.

202
00:07:09,864 --> 00:07:13,083
Yeah, it is;
Being nice sucks.

203
00:07:14,402 --> 00:07:16,569
