of the Warblers.

208
00:07:33,104 --> 00:07:35,088
I knew they'd send you.

209
00:07:35,106 --> 00:07:38,091
Allow me to answer
the obvious questions.

210
00:07:38,109 --> 00:07:41,862
I'm Hunter Clarington, I am
the new captain of the Warblers,

211
00:07:41,896 --> 00:07:43,697
and I'm not even
remotely bi-curious.

212
00:07:43,731 --> 00:07:45,065
How are you captain
of the Warblers when...?

213
00:07:45,099 --> 00:07:46,933
