to be with Kurt,

236
00:08:28,309 --> 00:08:29,409
right?

237
00:08:29,444 --> 00:08:30,444
In fact,

238
00:08:30,478 --> 00:08:34,948
I hear they even call you
Blaine Warbler.

239
00:08:34,982 --> 00:08:36,950
