242
00:08:41,289 --> 00:08:44,157
ambitious, driven.

243
00:08:44,175 --> 00:08:45,492
You're a Dalton boy.

244
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:47,660
Present the blazer.

245
00:08:50,131 --> 00:08:52,099
That's not going to work on me.
Then why be afraid

246
00:08:52,133 --> 00:08:53,350
to try it on?

247
00:09:03,695 --> 00:09:05,678
Here's the thing, Blaine.

248
00:09:05,697 --> 00:09:08,315
You know that Nationals
trophy was a fluke,

249
00:09:08,349 --> 00:09:12,319
just like you know we're
going to win at Sectionals.

250
00:09:12,353 --> 00:09:16,123
Now, I don't want to see
a Dalton legend like you

251
00:09:16,157 --> 00:09:19,025
